items.title: Trump Media to merge with fusion power company TAE Technologies in $6 billion deal
items.description: Trump Media and Technology Group announced a merger agreement with fusion power company TAE Technologies valued at more than $6 billion.

items.title: Trump announces 'warrior dividend' of $1,776 to every U.S. soldier in primetime speech
items.description: Trump highlighted his administration's efforts to seal the Southern border, bring down costs and strengthen U.S. foreign policy.

items.title: Epstein accomplice Ghislaine Maxwell petitions to vacate sex crime conviction
items.description: The habeas petition by Ghislaine Maxwell comes two day before a deadline for the Department of Justice to release files about Jeffrey Epstein.

items.title: FBI Deputy Director Dan Bongino is stepping down in January
items.description: Bongino had been selected by President Donald Trump for the high-profile law enforcement job despite him having no prior FBI experience.
